*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.so

# Node.js (if any web components)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Compiled JavaScript (if applicable)
*.js.map
*.tsbuildinfo
```